{"type": "article", "id": 46544, "title": "汉堡王又嘲讽麦当劳了，H&M 广告大片可以说是美轮美奂 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-10-26T04:03:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 15783, "name": "赵丽颖"}, {"id": 1628, "name": "汉堡王"}, {"id": 154, "name": "奥迪"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 126, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171026111725fiM2dwun37VUkA9D.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939} </style>  </p><h3>明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23709.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>赵丽颖出任格力高百奇代言人</b></a>，并拍摄了一支广告片，天猫上还推出了颖宝 Pocky 魔盒。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=r1326dfj19b&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/10/25/jingboran-and-masichun-become-chief-energy-officer-and-start-a-vigourous-trip/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>新晋奥迪 A3 形象大使井柏然和马思纯给奥迪拍了一支广告片</b></a>，扮演“A3能量使者”驱车进入二次元世界祛除负能量，短片使用了大量手绘漫画的元素。这支视频广告由良仓为奥迪制作的。良仓此前也为其他汽车品牌如宝马、雷克萨斯、别克、奔驰等做过创意视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z05652d814x&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42473\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>舒洁 VIVA 厨房纸巾的广告片《一秒顺媳养成班》</b></a>，把婆媳间的明争暗斗拍得还蛮好笑的。正赶上宜家广告风波的当口，也可以看看家庭伦理主题的广告可以怎么拍。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c0560ah6xvc&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42466\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>蔡康永给美加净的新品护手霜写了首歌，</b></a>据说创作灵感来自蔡康永的母亲，旋律听起来还挺活泼。</p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0024fqmbz2&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/burger-king-will-give-free-whoppers-to-people-dressed-as-clowns-on-halloween/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>汉堡王针对麦当劳做了个万圣节恐怖广告</b></a>，广告里充满了各种恐怖的小丑（影射麦当劳叔叔），还宣布万圣节期间只要打扮成小丑来汉堡王，可以得到免费汉堡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710261137271TVzCLuh8wBXGaAi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.478125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://v.qq.com/x/page/w0564a3rjse.html?start=2\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>H&amp;M 和伦敦设计师 Erdem 的联名合作系列发布了一支美轮美奂的广告片</b></a>，描述了一个充满春日光景的庄园发生的年轻而梦幻的爱情故事。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0564a3rjse&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.booooooom.com/2017/10/23/wardrobe-snacks-by-creative-duo-michelle-maguire-kelsey-mcclellan/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>俄亥俄造型师 Michelle Maguire 和旧金山的摄影师 Kelsey McClellan 合作拍摄了一套衣服和食物的图片“Wardrobe Snacks” </b></a>，挺好看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026114038NJH0k6SK1pCoWm75.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026114051Wu1Xj5JBzGa6e2q9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026114100bVWpZmtX65BMwJlL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017102611410864U82xbusLg1aiHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171026114116tBOxYi3zTZwSyMqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710261141230K4PhyfkxngUvuwS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>公司又有什么事儿发生</h3><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/a/hot/7543022671108097_1.html?type=new\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微博公布 2017 财年三季度未审计报告</b></a>，营收 3.2 亿美元，同比增长 80.9%，其中广告收入 2.768 亿美元。来自中小企业和关键客户的广告和营销营收为 2.515 亿美元；来自阿里巴巴的广告和营销营收为 2530 万美元。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：H&amp;M<b>&nbsp;</b>视频截图</p>"}